.ident	"@(#)proto:locale/C/menus/help/dtcontinent	1.4"
.related kbhelp genhelp datetime
.title Help: Continent
ABOUT THE CONTINENT MENU
Use this menu to view or change the current timezone setting.

CHANGING THE CONTINENT AND TIMEZONE
To change the continent (area) use the <Tab> or arrow keys to
move the asterisk to the appropriate field; then press <Enter>.

A list of timezone choices for the selected area appears.
An asterisk (*) is displayed next to the current timezone.
To change the timezone use the <Tab> or arrow keys to move
the asterisk to the appropriate field; then press <Enter>.

EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Continent menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
